1. *Onim* istim stolom svi se slažu. (They all agree with that same table.) 
2. Ova soba je *onim* iz prethodne sobe. (This room is the one from the previous room.) 
3. On je uzeo *onim* koferom. (He took that suitcase.) 
4. Ona je zagrlila *onim* čovekom. (She hugged that man.) 
5. *Onim* istim putem smo išli. (We went the same way.)